                "title": "盤繞風引"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素傷害</span>，<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">捨棄</span>手牌中所有的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">噬骸能量塊</span>，每<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">捨棄</span>2張，此次傷害翻倍1次。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/25/125391187/1d8d506cdab76fd7660ea285c094d231_2372761412499203591.png",
                "key": "錯落風渦",
                "materials": [],
